00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,520
Elyan?

611
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:19,440
What has she done to you?

612
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,760
No, don't.

613
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,120
It will not

614
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:22,120
let you pass.

615
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,880
<i>Morgana has enchanted it</i>

616
00:36:23,840 --> 00:36:25,880
<i>to protect me.</i>

617
00:36:25,920 --> 00:36:27,160
<i>You can't free me, elyan.</i>

618
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,320
Leave me here, please.

619
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,320
No.

620
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,560
You cannot

621
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,560
overcome it.

622
00:36:30,600 --> 00:36:31,560
It will fight

623
00:36:30,600 --> 00:36:31,560
to the death.

624
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:33,080
(Grunts)

625
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,000
(Gasps)

626
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:57,480
Elyan, go!

627
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:57,480
Save yourself.

628
00:37:07,040 --> 00:37:08,120
<i>(Clanging)</i>

629
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:12,400
(Exhales)

630
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,440
-<i> Gwen? </i>

631
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,440
- Elyan?

632
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,880
(Grunts)

633
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:27,480
I'm here. I'm here.

634
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:29,040
I'm here.

635
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:35,480
For a moment...

636
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:37,160
I didn't think

637
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:37,160
I was gonna win.

638
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:43,320
Father would be

639
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:43,320
proud of you.

640
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,640
And of you.

641
00:37:48,680 --> 00:37:51,240
(Chuckles)

642
00:37:51,280 --> 00:37:52,280
So proud.

643
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,560
(Exhales)

644
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:03,000
(Sobbing)

645
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:36,200
<i>I was warned one of us</i>

646
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:36,200
<i>would not return.</i>

647
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,800
It's not your fault,

648
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,800
Merlin.

649
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:44,000
Elyan is dead.

650
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,920
The sword that elyan

651
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,920
fell prey to

652
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,880
was surely intended

653
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:47,880
for Arthur.

654
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,040
Now he's safe.

655
00:39:52,080 --> 00:39:53,800
<i>And so is Gwen.</i>

656
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,400
How is it?

657
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,440
Arthur thinks he's won.

658
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:19,120
He has no idea.

659
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:22,240
Do you understand now

660
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:22,240
who you can trust?

661
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:24,840
It's you, morgana.

662
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,280
It's only ever been you.

663
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:28,320
You're not one of them,

664
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,640
and you never

665
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,640
will be.

666
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,680
You don't know

667
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:32,680
how much I hate them.

668
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:35,440
All of them.

669
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:37,600
You've done well

670
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:37,600
