671
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:37,600
to the real truth.

672
00:41:37,640 --> 00:41:41,040
You have an important part

673
00:41:37,640 --> 00:41:41,040
to play in the future.

674
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:43,240
Together we will ensure

675
00:41:41,080 --> 00:41:43,240
the destruction

676
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,800
of everything

677
00:41:43,280 --> 00:41:44,800
Arthur holds dear.

